      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, wash and shred your <strong>lettuce </strong>finely, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>into rounds</p>",
