    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> warmed pitta</strong> in half and spread the inside of each half with a dollop of <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, then stuff with the <strong>peri peri chicken</strong>, <strong>caramelised onions</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>rounds</strong> – this is your is your <strong>peri peri chicken pitta</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>peri peri chicken pitta </strong>with the <strong>sweet potato wedges </strong>and any <strong>remaining shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>tomato rounds</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
